{"tid":1834242,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"你咁做，我地係唔會取消架！！［求上熱門］","createTime":"2020-01-22T09:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T12:55:50.000Z","uid":121029,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"27b963865491ea370ab5a2472d06e291edde9201","tid":1834242,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我地喺旺角搞左個年宵，詳見以下帖：<br />\n<br />\n［突發］MK仔女自己年宵，自己搞！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801745</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雖然，由搞活動至今，日程又冇擺我地、又冇咩人知，不過我地本著一個大家開心過新年嘅心態去努力籌備，點知⋯喺活動嘅前夕終於出問題⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出讓舖位畀我地搞一日年宵嘅黃店，昨日起陸續有一堆自稱旺角警署嘅人上各店搵負責人，冇講咩事！今日又有食環上去鋪頭，表明活動已揚左畀政府，當日一定會嚟「巡」視！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我地有d擔心，不過⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺呢到，我地呢個活動宣佈如常進行！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地搞年宵大家開心，冇對人唔著！ 比我地做一日happy伯都唔得咩！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家好希望各位可以幫幫手！當日做下排隊師，等下𨋢上嚟參與下。大家記著自備環保袋同口罩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地好需要人流，好需要人流，好需要人流</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入面嘅遊戲同禮物，我地都諗左好耐，籌備左好耐！好希望大家喺咁難過嘅時間，年宵𠴱日會開心dd,放鬆一日就好了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMk 除左有MK仔女，仲有女僕一齊迎新年。<br />\n想知年宵點玩，請睇下列link:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200120/PHRY6NTAVJMTVAKZCHM6XPGJSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200120%2FPHRY6NTAVJMTVAKZCHM6XPGJSE%2F&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=7b7c5d70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200120%2FPHRY6NTAVJMTVAKZCHM6XPGJSE%2F&h=0f8f2e1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200120/PHRY6NTAVJMTVAKZCHM6XPGJSE/</a><br />\n<br />\n[堅離地年宵市集］Fever Fes. -離地年宵-<br />\n<br />\n1月24日 年三十 星期五 14:00-01:00<br />\n遊走旺角一帶4個場館合共50個攤位<br />\n投入RPG風格的設定<br />\n享受擺攤/尋寶的樂趣！！<br />\n<br />\n提供場地單位：<br />\nA.T FIELD CAFE<br />\nMaid Planet メイドプラネット<br />\nThe Bare Bones-異世界メイドギルド<br />\nYM Studio<br />\n<br />\n📍更多詳情請密切留意我們的專頁啊📖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/feverfes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffeverfes%2F&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=2c5f36cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/feverfes/</a><br />\nIg :fever.fes<br />\nTg:@NoAcc"},{"pid":"215689736ec89ad21c6bdefd9541e4bdb2a18d49","tid":1834242,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4hu2uG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4hu2uG.jpg&h=2c507b08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80eab9a208956ba2c7cbc890b52a5700001ecd6e","tid":1834242,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evVXrXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevVXrXL.jpg&h=13ee5421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d5782fb9ce7c27cf368d3cf93845aa026e336bb","tid":1834242,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"有冇同其他年宵撞<br />\n你需要人流 人地上埋日程表果d都需要<br />\n協調好重要"},{"pid":"4711a66ad3d78c9f4e97fa4bfc439c