edBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"當然政府年宵都唔係得一個地方啦<br />\n但係我睇你3個地方都係女僕cafe好似難搞d喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"有邊個event 係客易搞？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n租公開場地有公場地嘅難處，我地連女僕cafe都用埋係因為冇資源冇channel合作，自己細團體做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難搞唔緊要，最緊要你地嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63cdfb7231971b9c5e95c5b6136c0849de01f09","tid":1834242,"uid":240861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e3fcc144fb4351a42152804ff462df6a788cd0c","tid":1834242,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad670c63fb241d226601ff5db5ac1db23099b52","tid":1834242,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"正！！！"},{"pid":"30e1a5f737bfb4dfd4ee9f2aefd34ac4cd014d80","tid":1834242,"uid":262000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"唔同channel合作好難宣傳"},{"pid":"314d093070070aa4a45ead9f2b8595b7acbf516a","tid":1834242,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e1a5f737bfb4dfd4ee9f2aefd34ac4cd014d80","tid":1834242,"uid":262000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"唔同channel合作好難宣傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"毒呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，自己儘力做，問心無愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係求大家好需要人流幫手，我地規模咁細都比政府搞，係咪政府咁客納唔到私營活動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":